Nigerian Court Rules in Favor of Bank PHB Sale, the Nation Says

-- B y   E l i s h a   B a l a - G b o g b o
-- 
2011-06-09T08:20:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-09/nigerian-court-rules-in-favor-of-bank-phb-sale-the-nation-says.html
Nigeria’s Federal High Court in the
commercial capital, Lagos, dismissed a suit filed by five
shareholders to stop the central bank’s sale of  Bank PHB Plc (PLATINUM)  to
Pakistan’s  Habib Bank Ltd. (HBL) , the Nation reported, citing Justice
Charles Archibong.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Elisha Bala-Gbogbo in Abuja at 
 ebalagbogbo@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net . 